This study will enroll subjects with previously-treated advanced or inoperable gastric cancer who have responded to first line platinum therapy into two treatment arms.

 In Arm A subjects will receive BGB-290; in Arm B subjects will receive placebo.

 The purpose of this study is to show that BGB-290 (versus placebo) will improve progression-free survival (PFS) in subjects with advanced or inoperable gastric cancer.

